OL,5, Police chiefs have defended a 43%      
OL,6, year-on-year rise in the number of     
OL,7, officers based in UK schools.          
OL,9,FThe Runnymede Trust race equality think
OL,10,Ftank found 979 Safer Schools Officers  
OL,11,F(SSOs) in schools last spring, compared
OL,12,Fwith 683 in 2021.                      
OL,14,FIt found SSOs are more likely to be    
OL,15,Fbased in schools with higher numbers of
OL,16,Fchildren on free school meals, often   
OL,17,Fwith higher numbers of black pupils.   
OL,19,FBut the National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,20,Fsays SSOs play an essential role.      
